<br>
2) Planar Advancement. I'm hoping that our Planar advancement skills would set us more offensively oriented than say Enchanters PA would. This would certainly shift how a lower point damage nuke (Black Steel) would behave compared to a slightly higher one (Insanity). Who knows, at this point.<br>
<br>
